<li id="cite_note-18"><b><a href="#cite_ref-18" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFvan_Bon.2C_J..28Editor.292002">van Bon, J.(Editor) (2002). <i>The guide to IT service management</i>. Addison Wesley. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0201737922" class="internal">ISBN 0-201-73792-2</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+guide+to+IT+service+management&amp;rft.aulast=van+Bon%2C+J.%28Editor%29&amp;rft.au=van+Bon%2C+J.%28Editor%29&amp;rft.date=2002&amp;rft.pub=Addison+Wesley&amp;rft.isbn=0-201-73792-2&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Information_Technology_Infrastructure_Library"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-19"><b><a href="#cite_ref-19" title="">^</a></b> Meyer, Dean, 2005. <a href="http://web.archive.org/web/20050404165524/http://www.cio.com/leadership/buzz/column.html?ID=4186" class="external text" title="http://web.archive.org/web/20050404165524/http://www.cio.com/leadership/buzz/column.html?ID=4186" rel="nofollow">"Beneath the Buzz: ITIL"</a>, <i>CIO Magazine,</i> <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="2005-03-31"><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="03-31"><a href="/wiki/March_31" title="March 31">March 31</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/2005" title="2005">2005</a></span></li>
